                                       -----------------------------------
                                       Diamond 3 Plasma Theme Changelog
                                       -----------------------------------

Diamond v. 3.0.2

- Improved contrast slider
- Improved contrast listitem
- Updated documentation
                                       
                                       
                                       

Diamond v. 3.0.1

- Improved contrast buttons
- Improved contrast of the taskbar
- Other fix
- Updated documentation


                                       

Diamond v. 3.0 (2018-09-07)

- KDE 5.1x compatible
- Revised the various elements of the theme
- New decoration for taskbar
- Revised buttons colors
- Improved contrast
- Better color in scrollbars for usability
- Improved notification icon
- Updated documentation
- Added new widget clock
- Added volume icon
- Added vlc icon
- Other fix
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                            
 


                                        
                                        
                               
















                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                      
